spec_data.Name: easytag-nautilus
spec_data.Description:
Nautilus extension to add "Open with EasyTAG" to the Nautilus context menu, for
easier access to EasyTAG when opening directories and audio files.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 07 Aug 2017 01:10:27 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Nautilus extension for opening in EasyTAG
